@@gMONK@@W

Monks are disciplined impact-fighters who convert breath control and posture
mastery into relentless unarmed pressure.

@@gPassive class advantages@@W
  * @@wBare-hand direct-hit damage@@W bonus (+1% per level, up to +100% at 100).
  * @@wMartial strike damage@@W bonus for palmstrike/pummel/aurabolt family
    (+0.5% per level, up to +50% at 100).

@@gUnique Monk mechanics@@W
  * Access to @@wMonk stance@@W.
  * High unarmed scaling and strong chi-path synergy into Martial Artist.
  * Uses @@wConstitution@@W as prime remort attribute.

@@gMonk reincarnation bonuses@@W
  * @@wBrawler + Monk remort reincarnations >= 20@@W unlocks
    @@wEquip Fist@@W and @@wDual Fist@@W permanently.

See also: @@mremort stance brawler martial_artist chi reincarnate@@W
